  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Fulfilled revised European US consensus criteria for pSS

          -  Seropositive at screening for anti-Ro/SSA antibodies

          -  Documented salivary/lacrimal gland biopsy result confirming pSS diagnosis prior to the
             baseline visit

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Secondary Sjogren's syndrome

          -  Use of other investigational drugs

          -  Active viral, bacterial or other infections

          -  Positive hepatitis B, hepatitis C, HIV or tuberculosis test results at screening
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
